data.name: GetPropertyTolerantResult
desc: specifies information being retrieved about a single property.

items.name: Result
lines: specifies a success or error code for the retrieval operation.

items.name: State
lines: contains the state of the property.
The value is undefined if Result is not com.sun.star.beans.TolerantPropertySetResultType.SUCCESS.

items.name: Value
lines: contains the value of the property.
The value is undefined if Result is not com.sun.star.beans.TolerantPropertySetResultType.SUCCESS.
